MOD = 00

| R/M | Meaning                       |
| --- | ----------------------------- |
| 000 | `[BX + SI]`                   |
| 001 | `[BX + DI]`                   |
| 010 | `[BP + SI]`                   |
| 011 | `[BP + DI]`                   |
| 100 | `[SI]`                        |
| 101 | `[DI]`                        |
| 110 | **`[disp16]`** ← special case |
| 111 | `[BX]`                        |

Segment default:
[BP + ...] → SS
others → DS

